General.Name: Leeds Group PLC
General.Description: Leeds Group plc engages in the design, import, warehousing, and wholesale of fabrics. The company operates through two segments: Hemmers and KMR. It offers a range of fabrics comprising basic and fashion items for use in apparel or furnishings. The company is also involved in the retailing of fabric and haberdashery, as well as operates leased shops in Germany. It serves retailers and small wholesalers of fabrics; and manufacturers of ready-made items. Leeds Group plc serves customer in the United Kingdom and Europe. Leeds Group plc was incorporated in 1900 and is based in Leeds, the United Kingdom.
